{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "2.000", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe B\u00fcrger! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "2.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "4.800", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Frau Pr\u00e4sidentin! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "4.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.960", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.000", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Man kann sich dem Thema \u201eSteuervermeidung und Paradise Papers\u201c grunds\u00e4tzlich von zwei Seiten n\u00e4hern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "27.800", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Man kann nat\u00fcrlich dar\u00fcber lamentieren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "27.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "30.720", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass anderswo die Steuern viel zu niedrig sind. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "30.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "32.520", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Man kann aber auch die Frage stellen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "32.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.320", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob die Steuern bei uns nicht zu hoch sind."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "46.920", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Laut einer neuen Studie der OECD zieht der Staat bei uns fast 50\u00a0Prozent des Durchschnittseinkommens an Steuern und Abgaben ein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "46.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.640", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und die Umsatzsteuer ist da noch nicht drin. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.800", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damit sind wir Weltspitze. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.120", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Hier liegt das Problem, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.880", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und nicht woanders."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "54.480", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir brauchen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "54.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "55.560", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn Sie so wollen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "55.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "66.200", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Paradise Papers auch f\u00fcr Otto Normalb\u00fcrger und Otto Normalunternehmer in Deutschland oder besser eine durchgreifende Steuerreform mit einer klaren Entlastung."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "66.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "70.800", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Lasst den Deutschen endlich mehr von ihrem hart verdienten Geld in der Tasche."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "70.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "76.160", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber das kriegen Sie eben seit Jahrzehnten nicht auf die Reihe."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "76.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "77.960", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich erinnere mich noch an die 90er-Jahre: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "77.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "79.840", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "War nix mit der gro\u00dfen Steuerreform! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "79.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "81.640", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie kamen einfach nicht zu Potte. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "81.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "85.320", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Steuererkl\u00e4rung auf dem Bierdeckel von Friedrich Merz ist auch versandet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "85.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "91.840", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und 2005 wurde Professor Kirchhof mit Schimpf und Schande von Frau Merkel entsorgt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "91.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "96.160", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bis heute ist in Sachen Steuerreform nichts Wesentliches passiert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "96.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "104.400", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben nach wie vor eines der komplexesten Steuersysteme der Welt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "104.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "106.360", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Da ist es nat\u00fcrlich kein Wunder, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "106.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "111.760", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn sich die sogenannten Reichen mit ihren Heerscharen an Steuerberatern die passenden Schlupfl\u00f6cher suchen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "111.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "114.200", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "w\u00e4hrend Kleinverdiener und Mittelstand in die R\u00f6hre schauen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "114.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "115.800", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und das ist in der Tat ungerecht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "115.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "122.520", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dazu kommt die kalte Progression, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "122.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "124.000", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die endlich abgeschafft geh\u00f6rt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "124.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "125.520", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das wird nur nicht gemacht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "125.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "129.480", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil sie dem Finanzminister immer weiter steigende Einnahmen beschert."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "129.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "133.880", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "So wird der Spitzensteuersatz heute schon bei mittleren Verdienern f\u00e4llig. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "133.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "135.920", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Fr\u00fcher galt er erst bei Geh\u00e4ltern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "135.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "139.440", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die mindestens 15-mal so hoch waren wie der Durchschnittslohn. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "139.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "143.760", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Heute zahlt man den Spitzensteuersatz bereits bei dem 1,3-Fachen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "143.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "147.280", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Normalb\u00fcrger ist klar zur Melkkuh der Nation geworden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "147.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "148.680", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das m\u00fcssen wir \u00e4ndern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "148.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "151.640", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Daran arbeiten wir als AfD. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "151.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "154.520", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Eine Entlastung ist ja m\u00f6glich. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "154.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "159.520", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "W\u00e4hrend den B\u00fcrgern seit Jahren durch die Niedrigzinspolitik der EZB Milliarden entgehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "159.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "161.920", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "genau genommen Hunderte Milliarden,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "161.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "165.240", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "spart der Bund Milliarden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "165.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "167.520", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es entstehen Jahr f\u00fcr Jahr \u00dcbersch\u00fcsse, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "167.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "168.200", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und es geh\u00f6rt sich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "168.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.680", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass davon etwas an die Steuerzahler zur\u00fcckgegeben wird."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "180.320", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn wir die eigenen Hausaufgaben hier bei uns gemacht haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "180.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "184.440", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann k\u00f6nnen wir uns auch um einen fairen internationalen Steuerwettbewerb k\u00fcmmern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "184.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "186.720", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Da kann man nat\u00fcrlich \u00fcber manche Dinge reden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "186.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "193.440", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber der hier insbesondere von der linken Seite des Plenums vorgeschlagene Mindeststeuersatz w\u00e4re ein falscher Ansatz; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "193.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "195.840", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn er hebelt den Wettbewerb aus, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "195.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "197.520", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und der ist absolut wichtig. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "197.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "201.280", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ansonsten werden Politiker n\u00e4mlich zu schnell zu bequem."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "201.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "203.240", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Solange sie sich keine Gedanken machen m\u00fcssen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "203.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "208.680", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Unternehmen ins Ausland abwandern k\u00f6nnten,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "208.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "214.600", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "so lange haben sie nicht mehr als die blo\u00dfe Einnahmenmaximierung im Kopf. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "214.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "218.880", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wettbewerb ist eben ein Korrektiv zur Politik und deshalb wichtig."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "218.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "221.920", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es geht hier auch um Souver\u00e4nit\u00e4t. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "221.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "228.320", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das sage ich insbesondere in Richtung SPD. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "228.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "233.080", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Budgetrecht ist das heilige Recht eines jeden nationalen Parlamentes. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "233.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "234.440", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie k\u00f6nnen sich sicher sein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "234.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "235.160", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass dieses Recht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "235.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "236.280", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "insbesondere im Ausland, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "236.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "238.960", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "niemand an der Garderobe abgeben wird. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "238.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "243.800", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auf solche komischen Ideen kommen offensichtlich nur deutsche Tagtr\u00e4umer, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "243.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "247.400", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die auf Biegen und Brechen die Vereinigten Staaten von Europa erzwingen wollen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "247.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "249.000", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber das ist ein Irrweg. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "249.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "250.120", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir bitten Sie: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "250.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "251.960", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kehren Sie schnellstens um."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "251.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "254.320", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "254.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "258.160", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es l\u00e4sst sich trefflich \u00fcber unfaire Steuerbedingungen reden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "258.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "262.400", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber diese Art von Steuervermeidung wird es immer geben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "262.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "267.520", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das werden wir wirklich nur begrenzt beeinflussen k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "267.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "270.040", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb macht es keinen Sinn,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "270.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "275.000", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "heute hier mit vier Antr\u00e4gen Nebelkerzen zu z\u00fcnden und den B\u00fcrgern zu suggerieren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "275.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "277.560", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir k\u00f6nnten da von heute auf morgen Grundlegendes \u00e4ndern."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "277.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "280.760", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "K\u00fcmmern Sie sich lieber um unser eigenes, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "280.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "283.160", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dringend sanierungsbed\u00fcrftiges Steuersystem. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "283.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "285.760", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Baustelle ist wirklich gro\u00df genug."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "285.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "288.800", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Entlasten Sie die B\u00fcrger und Unternehmen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "288.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "292.640", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir als AfD-Fraktion sehen das jedenfalls als unsere Aufgabe an."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "292.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "300.320", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herzlichen Dank und Ihnen allen ein sch\u00f6nes Weihnachtsfest."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "300.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "302.160", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "302.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "306.840", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "N\u00e4chster Redner in der Debatte: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "306.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "310.000", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Michael Theurer f\u00fcr die FDP-Fraktion."
   ]
  }
 ]
}